headline: Nvidia, Alibaba, CrowdStrike, Snowflake, Inflation, and More to Watch This Week
summary: HP, Chewy, Alibaba, Best Buy, Dollar General, and more also will report earnings. On the economic front, we’ll see inflation numbers from several sources and a housing data release.
